'''可果美株式会社'''（カゴメ株式会社，KAGOME CO.,LTD.）是[[日本|日本]]一家以番茄为原料的食品和[[蔬果汁|蔬果汁]]制造商和经销商。其核心产品是1995年推出的{{link-ja|野菜生活100}}[[蔬菜汁|蔬菜汁]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.flex-news-food.com/pages/15929/Beverages/Japan/kagome-hike-prices-vegetable-juice-july-dj.html|title=Kagome to Hike Prices on Vegetable Juice in July (DJ)|date=2008-04-22|accessdate=2008-05-12|author=Dow Jones Newswires|authorlink=Dow Jones Newswires|publisher=FlEXNEWS|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080429212401/http://www.flex-news-food.com/pages/15929/Beverages/Japan/kagome-hike-prices-vegetable-juice-july-dj.html|archivedate=2008-04-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。可果美是日本最大的[[番茄酱|番茄酱]]和[[番茄汁|番茄汁]]供应商<ref name="english">{{Cite web
| url=http://www.kagome.co.jp/english/index.html
